data.description: Beautiful, spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in a desirable neighborhood just minutes from Tradition, I-95, shopping, schools, and so much more. NO HOA! Enter through the foyer into a large open-concept floorplan featuring wood-like tile throughout main living area. Main living area includes large living room, kitchen, and dining room. 2 bedrooms feature carpet while 2 bedrooms have LVP waterproof flooring. Open kitchen features a large island, pantry, stainless steel appliances, and a laundry/mudroom near the garage entrance. Living room leads out to a screened, enclosed patio and large backyard, complete with a wooden fence. 2 car garage. Home is 1,915 sq. ft. under air.
